  • jessicamanna79

    A great experience with a true pro!
    I am new to birding and booked this guide to learn about the birds of Tamil Nadu. It was a great experience that I would highly recommend to anyone - experienced pros, photographers, or those who are just starting out and curious, like me. Subu bought a great telescope and two sets of binoculars. The scope was high powered where I could see great detail of the eyes and feathers. He taught me about the calls of many birds and took me to two areas of the marshland. The part I enjoyed most was watching his kindness to others - there was a young couple watching us and he went over to explain about the birds, let them look through the scope, and offered to me the young man again to explain about the birds. That kind of passion is what builds a healthy birdwatching community by welcoming and bringing in new people. It’s not often a tour gets booked with such an accomplished professional - Subu records bird calls for international databases. It was a great time and I’m glad it worked out.
